@page "/BBDemo/FaIconDemo"

<PageTitle>图标演示</PageTitle>

<div class="container-fluid py-4 demo-page">
    <div class="card mb-3">
        <div class="card-header">
            <strong>BootstrapBlazorIcon 演示</strong>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
            <p class="text-muted mb-3">
                这个页面演示 `BootstrapBlazorIcon` 组件的基础用法，下面改成原生 `i` 标签，并把尺寸放大，方便查看效果。
                图标列表可以参考 <a href="https://fontawesome.com/icons" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Font Awesome Icons</a>。
            </p>

            <div class="row row-cols-2 row-cols-md-4 g-3">
                <div class="col">
                    <div class="border rounded bg-light text-center h-100 py-3">
                        <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center mb-2" style="font-size: 4rem; min-height: 5rem;">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-house"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="small text-muted">fa-solid fa-house</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                    <div class="border rounded bg-light text-center h-100 py-3">
                        <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center mb-2" style="font-size: 4rem; min-height: 5rem;">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-user"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="small text-muted">fa-solid fa-user</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                    <div class="border rounded bg-light text-center h-100 py-3">
                        <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center mb-2" style="font-size: 4rem; min-height: 5rem;">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-gear"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="small text-muted">fa-solid fa-gear</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                    <div class="border rounded bg-light text-center h-100 py-3">
                        <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center mb-2" style="font-size: 4rem; min-height: 5rem;">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-bell"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="small text-muted">fa-solid fa-bell</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                    <div class="border rounded bg-light text-center h-100 py-3">
                        <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center mb-2" style="font-size: 4rem; min-height: 5rem;">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-file-lines"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="small text-muted">fa-solid fa-file-lines</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                    <div class="border rounded bg-light text-center h-100 py-3">
                        <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center mb-2" style="font-size: 4rem; min-height: 5rem;">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="small text-muted">fa-solid fa-circle-info</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                    <div class="border rounded bg-light text-center h-100 py-3">
                        <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center mb-2" style="font-size: 4rem; min-height: 5rem;">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-heart"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="small text-muted">fa-solid fa-heart</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                    <div class="border rounded bg-light text-center h-100 py-3">
                        <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center mb-2" style="font-size: 4rem; min-height: 5rem;">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="small text-muted">fa-solid fa-star</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header">
            <strong>示例代码</strong>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
            <pre class="mb-0"><code>&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-house"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;
&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-user"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;
&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;</code></pre>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
